# need to change location 
vepPolygon <- polygon_from_extent(raster::extent(672800, 740000, 4102000, 4170000),
                                  proj4string = "+proj=utm +datum=NAD83 +zone=12")
NLCD_2011 <- get_nlcd(template = vepPolygon,
                 year = 2011,
                 dataset = "landcover",
                 label = "VEPIIN")
## Area of interest includes 1 NLCD tile(s).
## (Down)Loading NLCD tile: N36W108
## Downloading file: https://prd-tnm.s3.amazonaws.com/StagedProducts/NLCD/data/2011/landcover/3x3/NLCD2011_LC_N36W108.zip
raster::plot(NLCD_2011)
